{"tid":105395,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 8 於3月上市！新配色，規格、機型 曝光","createTime":"2017-02-03T00:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T07:26:59.000Z","uid":58099,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3aaf6ee7d520ab875f387b0fc9edacfbe6c1fbd2","tid":105395,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:24:54.000Z","msg":"2017年，迎接iPhone誕生十周年，蘋果全力以赴的iPhone 8 是重頭戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j8Ab3Yr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8Ab3Yr.jpg&h=461053b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無邊框<br />\n<br />\n蘋果曝光的新無邊框專利顯示，iPhone 8支持無邊框。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nA8Ea9B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnA8Ea9B.jpg&h=10d60f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n專利名「將光感傳感器嵌入到螢幕的一種方式」，能將光感傳感器整合放入螢幕各層之間，手機屏占比更大，實現無邊框。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MiVHe6B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMiVHe6B.jpg&h=940b577e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niPhone 8將擁有一個4K螢幕和底部雙揚聲器，而厚度為6.5毫米，整部手機的重量僅為115克。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18M0T12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18M0T12.jpg&h=f6e674f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟隨歷史軌跡<br />\n<br />\n配置4GB RAM，搭載A11核心以及運行iOS 11，1600萬像素後置攝像頭，支持無線充電。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/03/082132_1e10d72844cb6eb8012c37c2e95de363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F082132_1e10d72844cb6eb8012c37c2e95de363.jpg&h=c86c7590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n清新小功能<br />\n<br />\n機身背後的蘋果Logo，將作為一個輔助「螢幕」，提醒你收到簡訊，還能充當電池指示燈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZ267Ut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZ267Ut.jpg&h=4e746c28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新配色：葡萄酒<br />\n<br />\n因受亮黑色iPhone 7搶購刺激，蘋果將繼續推出新配色「葡萄酒」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/03/082205_c05ffd32c9a5dd6f68b48404061b61cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F082205_c05ffd32c9a5dd6f68b48404061b61cc.jpg&h=95ce9578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n規格<br />\n<br />\n- 單鏡頭為2,100萬像素，Plus則是搭載雙鏡頭2,200萬像素。<br />\n<br />\n- iPhone 8據為4.9吋，而iPhone 8 Plus將為6.2吋。<br />\n<br />\n- iPhone 8記憶體為4GB RAM、iPhone 8 Plus則是6GB RAM。"},{"pid":"7f0647f94c283353cfd92f94e4e48eb024bca614","tid":105395,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:30:20.000Z","msg":"醬汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79071810b0e752eb58ab0bfde163f4b6f71a5da","tid":105395,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:31:16.000Z","msg":"成編除左A11 ios11<br />\n冇樣正常  全部FF"},{"pid":"8214f7b3b489b9a6a081195fa5d5258813c6e952","tid":105395,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:31:49.000Z","msg":"D圖用左幾年，仲老過好多小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，點解會有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58e821b79f0006f51ddb5c1ec5facc1cd26542a","tid":105395,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:32:34.000Z","msg":"啱啱先轉左粒掣點會咁快無左，起碼玩多兩代"},{"pid":"78f0ba93b389874c248223bf595a2d6e40a28a6e","tid":105395,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:34:00.000Z","msg":"又有野炒"},{"pid":"5325e8ff490b66861b9af73d241e53fb4188e695","tid":105395,"uid":2455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"假野都有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39154fba5db5bc20ddb142fa3ac4c0087a9ee31a","tid":105395,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite